      type         : MACOSX_DEFAULTS_READ
      description  : "AOSX-10-000075 - Infrared [IR] support must be disabled."
      info         : "Infrared [IR] kernel support must be disabled to prevent users from controlling the system with IR devices. By default, if IR is enabled, the system will accept IR control from any remote."
      solution     : "To disable IR, run the following command:

